				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%C3%A1t-ai-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-8-C%E1%BB%91-h%E1%BB%AFu-b%E1%BB%99c-x%E1%BA%A1-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-qu%E1%BB%91c-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%E1%BB%ADu-Linh/poem-OMzIcEXGWASbO9P2feqjhw">Bát ai thi kỳ 8 - Cố hữu bộc xạ tướng quốc Trương Cửu Linh - 八哀詩其七－故右僕射相國張公九齡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/Bi%E1%BB%87n-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-t%E1%BB%91ng-L%C3%BD-D%C4%A9nh-chi-T%C3%B4-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-X16RMRbfCYrf-cHOndPdNg">Biện thượng tống Lý Dĩnh chi Tô Châu - 汴上送李郢之蘇州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/C%E1%BB%ADu-nh%E1%BA%ADt/poem-_CdS69n22mKys5miH53jxQ">Cửu nhật - 九日</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/D%E1%BB%B1-Ch%C3%A2u-ca/poem-b6Dd-0JV6ITuPc6E5eTHpQ">Dự Châu ca - 豫州歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Tr%E1%BA%A5n/%C4%90%C3%A1p-th%C3%A1i-t%E1%BB%AD-th%E1%BA%BF-t%E1%BB%AD-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-aLDm3J2ulw2L4MPFRbH8_Q">Đáp thái tử thế tử vận - 答太子世子韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Tr%E1%BA%A5n/author-CwltqHE1BE9nosYynwsu8g">Dương Đình Trấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/H%C6%B0ng-Kh%C3%A1nh-tr%C3%AC-th%E1%BB%8B-y%E1%BA%BFn-%E1%BB%A9ng-ch%E1%BA%BF/poem-RhDJEqPrqiE7CPf4zbLRSg">Hưng Khánh trì thị yến ứng chế - 興慶池侍宴應制</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/author-26T9AYFiJg6kLfVbUIq6cA">Vi Nguyên Đán</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/H%E1%BB%AFu-c%C3%A1-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C3%BA-t%C3%A0i/poem-iossNOnIWvWZ5kKBrPgVvw">Hữu cá Vương tú tài - 有個王秀才</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/author-o98HuijKnTRKdgvHyXbEYw">Hàn Sơn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%E1%BB%B1c/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-s%E1%BB%A9-%C4%91%C4%83ng-tr%C3%ACnh-t%E1%BB%B1-thu%E1%BA%ADt/poem-Jbo4CE9Vim98vO5_8l--SA">Phụng sứ đăng trình tự thuật - 奉使登程自述</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-KlUCS3ER6VvH2W9Ma4g25A">Nguyễn Thực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-M%E1%BA%A1nh-Trinh/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n-t%E1%BA%ADp-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-m8buZGd9acbui1906QmgWA">Thanh Tâm tài nhân tập tự - 青心才人詩集序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-M%E1%BA%A1nh-Trinh/author-ZpBj6D9P3q-U3JR36g_w5g">Chu Mạnh Trinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/Thu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-khi%E1%BB%83n-h%E1%BB%A9ng/poem-SMou7wV-0N8pix3G-Tg0ng">Thu nhật khiển hứng - 秋日遣興</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br></div>	</div>
